snippet.title: Tamarin - Adventure Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore, leap and shoot to save your family from the insect invasion! Leap with the agility of a tamarin as you journey into the Northern wilderness, in a world full of exploration, 3D-platforming and bug-splattering action!

For more information, visit the game's website or follow on social media:

Website: http://www.tamaringame.com/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/chameleon_games
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/chameleongames.ltd/

Tamarin is releasing Sept 10 2020 on PlayStation 4 and PC.
